channel.title: Wtf?
channel.description:
I like to play on the server, UPDATE Ninjaascape, but for the last 2 days I couldn't. I'll explain it too you, so yesterday I was on the Server Status Page and looking for Ninjaascape (Page 4, 2nd to last) I clicked on low detail and Java started loading. After Java was done loading, the files started to load, after about 5 seconds my screen turned black (except for advertisements), does anyone no what to do?
P.S. All the other servers do the same thing!

item.title: Wtf?
item.dc:creator: @Telenim Telenim
item.description:
@Telenim wrote:

Don’t use the web-client then, download a client such as MoparScape 3.2 or Silabsoft Client and attempt to run it.
